{"tid":1318854,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"NCT 127遠赴美國為新碟造勢 成員Mark遭當地人歧視","createTime":"2019-07-15T04:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T15:48:55.000Z","uid":170044,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"015d41f2da15b4632130c29b243c8b1a1254b69e","tid":1318854,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:42:26.000Z","msg":"韓國男團NCT 127將於5月27日推出第4張迷你專輯《We Are Superhuman》，近日NCT 127成員泰一、泰容、悠太、在玹、Mark、楷燦、Johnny、道英和廷祐在美國四出為新碟造勢，包括演出美國ABC節目《Good Morning America》，率先表現新歌《Superhuman》，以及在紐約街頭與當地粉絲近距離接觸。不過，有NCT 127成員在當地受到種族歧視，引起NCTzen（NCT粉絲）和韓國網民非議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2XWPJP9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2XWPJP9.png&h=6007282d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有民眾向Mark揮手示意後，隨即向他舉中指。（網上截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eo6zUWz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feo6zUWz.png&h=9ad92791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有女粉絲向Mark揮動3美金鈔票，令Mark相當驚奇。（網上圖片）"},{"pid":"f8a2f07afda7a3900f54171f2e69abd854a6518d","tid":1318854,"uid":170044,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:43:30.000Z","msg":"三蚊雞的意思　暗寸同性戀<br />\n<br />\n韓國網民在當地討論區「The qoo」發布名為「在美國遇到種族歧視的NCT」帖文，指NCT 127出席復活節活動後，有途人向Mark揮手，得到對方注意後，該名途人隨即向Mark舉中指；此外，NCT 127在19日完成工作，準備登上宣傳巴士離去時，有女粉絲向NCT 127揮動3張1元美金紙幣，在玹和Mark看見她手上的金錢均感到驚訝。內地傳媒形容該名粉絲是「NCT現金應援」，但更多網民認為該名女粉絲揮動3元美金是種族歧視，皆因3元美金有諷刺同性戀，或是用3元就能買下對方的的含意，所以有NCTzen不滿該名女粉絲的舉動，認為對NCT 127揮動3元美金與種族歧視無異。"},{"pid":"7aa821950aa689ca72f519b99b7a0bcd017d8b32","tid":1318854,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:47:08.000Z","msg":"第3個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16353bde93b76d683c8160e1eb120b285eee8d68","tid":1318854,"uid":171598,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dqYVEq8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdqYVEq8.gif&h=36c5b4e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18167f9caffe3b35b60d0494a1e0887b438957a3","tid":1318854,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aa821950aa689ca72f519b99b7a0bcd017d8b32","tid":1318854,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:47:08.000Z","msg":"第3個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:53:12.000Z","msg":"我係想搵下邊位巴打咁勇對住禾地牙mark舉中指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71b1fcd40f6e796da37b673b798b231deeb0815","tid":1318854,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:56:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d5Eo_HVWmDc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd5Eo_HVWmDc&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKUngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=aae16ae1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d5Eo_HVWmDc</a>"},{"pid":"0a04a49f7210664428e2ace3c2e39fe1d828ef29","tid":1318854,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T12:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688936d7b4f73b3f077cd9770a1f7cff0963971d","tid":1318854,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16353bde93b76d683c8160e1eb120b285eee8d68","tid":1318854,"uid":171598,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dqYVEq8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdqYVEq8.gif&h=36c5b4e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6fa9ad0b12b4c31bd26792c237b1e71f18ce01a","tid":1318854,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:48:55.000Z","msg":"慘"}]}